# TasteForge (Cursor)

Renaiss Hackathon MVP — deadline **July 11, 2026**.

## Project

AI agent + web app helping collectors find cards matching personal taste AND value.

## Key integrations

| Source | URL | Use |
|--------|-----|-----|
| Renaiss Marketplace API | `https://www.renaiss.xyz/api/trpc/collectible.list` | Live FMV, prices, images, owner lookup |
| renaiss-scanner | https://github.com/blueskylh/renaiss-scanner | Reference impl; optional scanner API |
| Scanner tool (deployed) | https://renaiss-tool-689931.napa.de5.net/ | Consecutive pair discovery UI |

## Architecture

```
Wallet paste → viem BNB validate → Renaiss marketplace owner scan
              → Taste Vector (LangGraph) → Resonance + Value scores
              → Best Overall / Best Value recommendations
```

## Code layout

- `src/lib/renaiss/` — marketplace client, scanner client, card mapping
- `src/lib/chain/` — viem BSC read-only
- `src/lib/agents/` — LangGraph pipeline
- `src/lib/taste-vector/` — resonance + value scoring
- `src/app/api/wallet` — wallet holdings
- `src/app/api/analyze` — full agent run

## Demo wallets

- Maya: `0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000001`
- Luca: `0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000002`
- Jordan: `0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000003`

## Conventions

- Read-only chain access only — never request private keys
- Mock fallback when live API fails (hackathon-safe demos)
- Keep UI dark collector theme (zinc/amber/rose)
- Prefer extending existing types in `src/lib/types/index.ts`

